if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	writefile_2();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') != '1ff735910263a99cccf6cbccd24293aedd911690') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '1ff735910263a99cccf6cbccd24293aedd911690') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '66bdeaa765c07722c4476a7e3641c1a214046864') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_2();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '1ff735910263a99cccf6cbccd24293aedd911690') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('vendor/composer/ClassLoader.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/composer/ClassLoader.php');
	writefile_14();
	if (!is_file('vendor/composer/ClassLoader.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/composer/ClassLoader.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/composer/ClassLoader.php') != 'd4a058aaad78183c3f2e53b04c63beb617c3f6db') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/ClassLoader.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/composer/ClassLoader.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/composer/ClassLoader.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/ClassLoader.php') !== 'd4a058aaad78183c3f2e53b04c63beb617c3f6db') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/ClassLoader.php') !== '8d9f47db4e033e631ebc6dc1f0bd282d23bdaa97') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/composer/ClassLoader.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/composer/ClassLoader.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/composer/ClassLoader.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/composer/ClassLoader.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_14();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/ClassLoader.php') !== 'd4a058aaad78183c3f2e53b04c63beb617c3f6db') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/ClassLoader.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('vendor/composer/InstalledVersions.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/composer/InstalledVersions.php');
	writefile_15();
	if (!is_file('vendor/composer/InstalledVersions.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/composer/InstalledVersions.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/composer/InstalledVersions.php') != '609c9766c9ca423203223982dce0b68b39205672') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/InstalledVersions.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/composer/InstalledVersions.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/composer/InstalledVersions.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/InstalledVersions.php') !== '609c9766c9ca423203223982dce0b68b39205672') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/InstalledVersions.php') !== 'f830564e2ff61101836a38bc4c873e2f50a958a8') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/composer/InstalledVersions.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/composer/InstalledVersions.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/composer/InstalledVersions.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/composer/InstalledVersions.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_15();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/InstalledVersions.php') !== '609c9766c9ca423203223982dce0b68b39205672') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/InstalledVersions.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/composer/LICENSE');
	writefile_16();
	if (!is_file('vendor/composer/LICENSE')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/composer/LICENSE');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/composer/LICENSE') != '38e062192cc23823bb2a279cb28c8a176d439b3b') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/LICENSE');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/composer/LICENSE', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/composer/LICENSE');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/LICENSE') !== '38e062192cc23823bb2a279cb28c8a176d439b3b') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/LICENSE') !== '8bff0b392ab60b65a95ecc07e1029d6d0d48261e') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/composer/LICENSE');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/composer/LICENSE');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/composer/LICENSE')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/composer/LICENSE', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_16();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/LICENSE') !== '38e062192cc23823bb2a279cb28c8a176d439b3b') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/LICENSE');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.json')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/composer/installed.json');
	writefile_18();
	if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.json')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/composer/installed.json');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') != '14e60e9fa40d9aa29505c8210bb966e92ba8bab4') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.json');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/composer/installed.json', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/composer/installed.json');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') !== '14e60e9fa40d9aa29505c8210bb966e92ba8bab4') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') !== '2e39ec62058ebb8dd18985ee9997b2e4655db67f') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/composer/installed.json');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/composer/installed.json');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/composer/installed.json')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/composer/installed.json', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_18();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.json') !== '14e60e9fa40d9aa29505c8210bb966e92ba8bab4') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.json');
		}
	}
}

// Files different: vendor/composer/installed.php

if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/composer/installed.php');
	writefile_19();
	if (!is_file('vendor/composer/installed.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/composer/installed.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') != 'f3bcfb066b7780e8ab902ade3ad5f678243c7c02') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/composer/installed.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/composer/installed.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') !== 'f3bcfb066b7780e8ab902ade3ad5f678243c7c02') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') !== '416453df480a6a9d07fab213da9d8f1b91487ff8') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/composer/installed.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/composer/installed.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/composer/installed.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/composer/installed.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_19();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/composer/installed.php') !== 'f3bcfb066b7780e8ab902ade3ad5f678243c7c02') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/composer/installed.php');
		}
	}
}

// Files different: vendor/licenses

if (!is_file('vendor/licenses')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: vendor/licenses');
	writefile_23();
	if (!is_file('vendor/licenses')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): vendor/licenses');
	} else if (sha1_file('vendor/licenses') != '270b8b552f95639c1ce900f7789a5459d96ffb56') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): vendor/licenses');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('vendor/licenses', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of vendor/licenses');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('vendor/licenses') !== '270b8b552f95639c1ce900f7789a5459d96ffb56') {
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/licenses') !== 'cafddf93d1724baf24234d935724bcefedd6a62f') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: vendor/licenses');
			$tmp = pathinfo('vendor/licenses');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('vendor/licenses')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('vendor/licenses', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_23();
		if (@sha1_file('vendor/licenses') !== '270b8b552f95639c1ce900f7789a5459d96ffb56') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): vendor/licenses');
		}
	}
}
